
Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I go to Page 05 of Thoracic CT
And I select 'Finding' radio button
And I select 'Consolidation' from the dropdown menu
And I select 'I describe' radio button

When I click on 'Characterization II' tab
Then 'Eccentric necrosis' checkbox is enabled
And 'Abscess' checkbox is enabled
And 'Cavitation' checkbox is enabled
And 'Hemorrhage' checkbox is enabled
And 'Pneumatocele' checkbox is enabled

And 'Halo sign' checkbox is enabled
And 'Reversed halo sign' checkbox is enabled
And 'Associated atelectasis' checkbox is enabled
And 'Accompanying effusion' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Cavitation' checkbox
Then 'Luftsichel sign' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Accompanying effusion' checkbox
Then 'Accompanying effusion' input field is enabled
